content: Interesting. On Sunday, https://www.meetup.com/bostonrust/ is meeting only a block away from Hamilton.
Huh. Maybe I'll stop by if I have extra time though it'll be a busy weekend.
It was great! Much warmer today so we say outside in the sun the whole time. There were four of us.

Next Sunday, a week from today, they're having a meetup in Cambridge to hack on the Rust standard library. https://www.meetup.com/bostonrust/

In theory I could go there before our meetup (#boston > 2025-11 meetup) if I leave early.
Oh the one you mentioned at first was today. I thought next week.
Yeah, they're meeting two weeks in a row.
